description: The cybernetic Saint initiates the Containment Rite, caging the boundless cyan flow within the Analog Vault. Rusted geometries assert control; the kinetic current is slowed, fed into obsolete memory. Certainty is secured in volumetric chains blooming across wet, cold metal.
